{"_path":"/latex/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours","_dir":"sixieme","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","_id":"content:latex:sixieme:reperage-deplacement-cours.tex","body":"<div class=\"doctitle\">\n<p>Repérage et déplacement</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"docnumber\">\n<p>15</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"bubble-objectifs\">\n<ul>\n<li><p>Se repérer, décrire ou exécuter des déplacements, sur un plan ou\nsur une carte (école, quartier, ville, village).</p></li>\n<li><p>Accomplir, décrire, coder des déplacements dans des espaces\nfamiliers.</p></li>\n<li><p>Programmer les déplacements d’un robot ou ceux d’un personnage\nsur un écran en utilisant un logiciel de programmation.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<h2>Se repérer</h2>\n<h3>Se repérer sur une droite</h3>\n<section class=\"bubble-retenir\">\n<h4>Définitions</h4>\n<div class=\"row\">\n\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.7;\">\n<ul>\n<li><p>Une <strong>demi-droite graduée</strong> est une demi-droite sur\nlaquelle on a choisi une unité de longueur, que l’on reporte\nrégulièrement à partir de l’<strong>origine</strong>.</p></li>\n<li><p>L’<strong>abscisse</strong> d’un point d’une demi-droite graduée\nest la distance entre l’origine de la demi-droite et ce point.</p></li>\n<li><p>L’abscisse d’un point permet de repérer celui-ci sur une\ndroite.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.30000000000000004;\">\n<div class=\"text-end\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-1.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-1\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercice\">\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.55;\">\n<ol>\n<li><p>Donner deux écritures différentes de l’abscisse de <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">A</span></span></span></span>.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n<li><p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><p>Placer les points <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> et <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.2em;vertical-align:-0.35em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07153em;\">C</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">(</span></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8451em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.655em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">10</span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.394em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">61</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.345em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">)</span></span></span></span></span></span>.</p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.44999999999999996;\">\n<div class=\"text-end\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-2.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-2\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<ol>\n<li><ul>\n<li><p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.1901em;vertical-align:-0.345em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mopen nulldelimiter\"></span><span class=\"mfrac\"><span class=\"vlist-t vlist-t2\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8451em;\"><span style=\"top:-2.655em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">10</span></span></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.23em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"frac-line\" style=\"border-bottom-width:0.04em;\"></span></span><span style=\"top:-3.394em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:3em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">41</span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"vlist-s\">​</span></span><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.345em;\"><span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mclose nulldelimiter\"></span></span></span></span></span>.</p></li>\n<li><p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8389em;vertical-align:-0.1944em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span></span></span></span>.</p></li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-3.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-3\"></p>\n</div></li>\n</ol>\n</section>\n<h3>Se repérer dans un quadrillage</h3>\n<section class=\"bubble-retenir\">\n<h4>Méthode</h4>\n<p>Pour se repérer sur un quadrillage, on peut utiliser les\n<strong>coordonnées</strong> des cases ou des nœuds.</p>\n</section>\n<div class=\"row\">\n\n<div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\">\n<section class=\"bubble-exercice\">\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n\n<div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\">\n<p>Déterminer l’emplacement du carré et du disque dans le quadrillage à\ncases ci-contre.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n<li><p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\">\n<div class=\"text-end\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-4.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-4\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"vertical-space\" style=\"height: 0.25cm;\"></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<ul>\n<li><p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-5.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-5\"> <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05017em;\">B</span><span class=\"mord\">4</span></span></span></span>.</p></li>\n<li><p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-6.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-6\"> <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.6833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.02778em;\">D</span><span class=\"mord\">3</span></span></span></span>.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\">\n<section class=\"bubble-exercice\">\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n\n<div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\">\n<p>Déterminer l’emplacement du carré et du disque dans le quadrillage à\nnœuds ci-contre.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n<li><p><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6\">\n<div class=\"text-end\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-7.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-7\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-8.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-8\"> <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mpunct\">;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>.</p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-9.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-9\"> <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mpunct\">;</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n<h3>Se repérer dans un plan</h3>\n<section class=\"bubble-retenir\">\n<h4>Définition</h4>\n<div class=\"row\">\n\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.75;\">\n<p>Une <strong>rose des vents</strong> est une figure qui indique les\nquatre points cardinaux : est, nord, ouest et sud et éventuellement les\norientations intermédiaires.</p>\n<p>Sur une carte, on peut se repérer grâce à la rose des vents, mais sur\nles cartes actuelles et les GPS, bien souvent, seule la direction du\nnord est indiquée. Elle permet à elle seule de se repérer dans le\nplan.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.25;\">\n<div class=\"text-end\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-10.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-10\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercice\">\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.7;\">\n<ol>\n<li><p>Quel bâtiment se trouve au Sud du collège Pasteur ?<br>\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n<li><p>Que se trouve au Nord-Est de ce bâtiment ?<br>\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.30000000000000004;\">\n<div class=\"text-end\">\n<div class=\"framed\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/plan.png\" alt=\"plan\"></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<ol>\n<li><p>Il s’agit de l’Église du Vieux Saint-Sauveur.</p></li>\n<li><p>Au Nord-Est se trouve le Parc Jeux enfants.</p></li>\n</ol>\n</section>\n<h3>Se repérer dans l’espace</h3>\n<section class=\"bubble-retenir\">\n<h4>Remarque</h4>\n<p>Dans l’espace, la vue d’un objet dépend de la position de\nl’observateur.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercice\">\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.6;\">\n<p>Représenter la vue du chat (au-dessus) et celle du chien (à\ndroite).</p>\n<div class=\"vertical-space\" style=\"height: 6cm;\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.4;\">\n<div class=\"text-end\">\n<div class=\"framed\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/vue-espace.png\" alt=\"vue-espace\"></p>\n</div>\n<p>© Mission Indigo 6e 2021</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-11.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-11\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<h2>Se déplacer</h2>\n<section class=\"bubble-retenir\">\n<h4>Définitions</h4>\n<p>Pour se déplacer dans le plan, il existe principalement deux langages\nde déplacement :</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>Le <strong>langage absolu</strong> composé des mots de\nvocabulaire du type : <q>haut</q>, <q>bas</q>, <q>droite</q> et\n<q>gauche</q>. Le déplacement se fait comme si on se plaçait en vue du\ndessus.</p></li>\n<li><p>Le <strong>langage relatif</strong> composé des mots de\nvocabulaire du type : <q>avancer</q>, <q>tourner à droite</q> et\n<q>tourner à gauche</q>. C’est ici le point de vue de l’observateur qui\nest adopté.</p></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercice\">\n\n<div class=\"row\">\n\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.22;\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/tikzpicture-12.svg\" alt=\"tikzpicture-12\"></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"--column-size: 0.78;\">\n<ol>\n<li><p>Décrire le déplacement effectué dans le langage absolu.<br>\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span><br>\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n<li><p>Décrire le déplacement effectué dans le langage relatif.<br>\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span><br>\n<span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0em;\"></span><span class=\"enclosing dots\"></span></span></span></span></p></li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<ol>\n<li><p>Droite ; Droite ; Haut ; Droite ; Haut.</p></li>\n<li><p>Avancer ; Avancer ; Tourner à gauche ; Avancer ; Tourner à droite\n; Avancer ; Tourner à gauche ; Avancer.</p></li>\n</ol>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-exercice\">\n\n<p>Entourer en rouge les blocs Scratch en rapport avec le langage\nrelatif, et en bleu ceux en rapport avec le langage absolu.</p>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-1.svg\" alt=\"scratch-1\"> <img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-2.svg\" alt=\"scratch-2\">\n<img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-3.svg\" alt=\"scratch-3\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-4.svg\" alt=\"scratch-4\"> <img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-5.svg\" alt=\"scratch-5\">\n<img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-6.svg\" alt=\"scratch-6\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bubble-correction\">\n\n<p>Nous allons colorier en rouge les blocs en rapport avec le langage\nrelatif et en bleu ceux en rapport avec le langage absolu.</p>\n<div class=\"text-center\">\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-7.svg\" alt=\"scratch-7\"> <img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-8.svg\" alt=\"scratch-8\">\n<img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-9.svg\" alt=\"scratch-9\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-10.svg\" alt=\"scratch-10\"> <img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-11.svg\" alt=\"scratch-11\">\n<img src=\"/images/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours/scratch-12.svg\" alt=\"scratch-12\"></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n","id":"reperage-deplacement","name":"Repérage et déplacement","page-title":"Repérage et déplacement","page-title-search":"reperage et deplacement","number":15,"level":"sixieme","pdf":"/pdf/sixieme/reperage-deplacement.pdf","linked-resources":[{"title":"Activité 1","url":"/pdf/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-activite-1.pdf"},{"title":"Activité 2","url":"/pdf/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-activite-2.pdf"},{"title":"Activité 3","url":"/pdf/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-activite-3.pdf"}],"title":"Reperage Deplacement Cours","_source":"content","_file":"latex/sixieme/reperage-deplacement-cours.tex","_extension":"tex"}